These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, funk
There 2 different types of food: nectarine, cucumber
The people have 2 different hobbies: hiking, camping
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, fonseca
1. the fonseca-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
2. the fan of funk is in an even position##4
3. the person eating cucumber is the fan of classical##1
4. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Music-Genre      | classical  | funk   |
| Food   | cucumber     | nectarine   |
| Hobby         | camping | hiking |
| Cigar     | dunhill | fonseca    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: chestnut, grey
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: rose, poppy
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: pop, house
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, iced-tea
1. the fan of house is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growsrose is the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Color          | chestnut     | grey |
| Flower   | poppy | rose  |
| Music-Genre           | house         | pop     |
| Beverage     | mirinda   | iced-tea    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: poppy, marigold
2 different games are played: go, snooker
There are 2 different favourite colors: green, blood-red
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, july
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
2. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
3. the person who growspoppy is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Flower    | marigold     | poppy |
| Game         | snooker | go    |
| Color         | green         | blood-red        |
| Birthday   | march         | july    |

