.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different nationalities: brazilian, argentine
The people have 2 different jobs:  electrician, doctor
2 different pets are kept: horse, rat
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, taxi
1. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
2. the doctor is on the left of the brazilian##1
3. the person driving the taxi is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Nationality      | argentine     | brazilian |
| Job          | doctor   | electrician  |
| Pet         | horse | rat     |
| Transport   | bus  | taxi         |

