.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: hip-hop, rock
City: san-francisco, nizza
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, cycling
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, november
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is in an odd position##4
3. the person traveling to nizza is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Music-Genre      | hip-hop | rock       |
| City           | nizza      | san-francisco     |
| Sport   | cycling       | snowboarding   |
| Birthday           | november          | april |

