.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
City: liverpool, new-york
There 2 different types of food: zucchini, carrot
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, superhero
1. the person watching superhero movies is in an even position##4
2. the person eating carrot is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person traveling to new-york is the person eating zucchini##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person eating carrot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| City           | new-york | liverpool    |
| Food   | zucchini       | carrot |
| Beverage           | fanta         | juice    |
| Movie-Genre         | thriller    | superhero   |

