.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-20::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: photography, drawing
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, june
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, poker
There 2 different types of food: nectarine, pumpkin
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person playing poker##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
3. the person eating nectarine is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Hobby    | photography | drawing    |
| Birthday         | june        | january |
| Game         | mah-jongg          | poker     |
| Food   | nectarine        | pumpkin     |

 